						"title": "Protecting patient data and healthcare continuity",
						"titleSize": null,
						"subtitle": "A growing digital attack surface demands a unified defense",
						"subtitleSize": null,
						"copy": "The shift to digital health, telehealth, and remote networks has exposed the healthcare industry to a surging tide of cyberattacks. Escalating third-party risks, an expanding attack surface, and rising data breaches are directly jeopardizing patient safety and care continuity. Your network demands a modern, unified defense.\n\n__How Cloudflare supports digital health operations:__\n\n<ul>\n  <li style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; margin: 0;\"><strong>Implement Zero Trust policies</strong>\nTo enable secure application access for telehealth and remote care workers.\n  </li>\n  <li style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; margin: 0;\"><strong>Prevent attacks</strong>\nOn critical patient-facing applications with comprehensive WAAP solutions.\n  </li>\n  <li style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; margin: 0;\"><strong>Safeguard networks</strong>\nAgainst the latest strains of malware and ransomware.\n  </li>\n  <li style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; margin: 0;\"><strong>Mitigate Third-Party risks</strong>\nBy maintaining consistent compliance controls across your ecosystem.\n  </li>\n</ul>\n",
